---

<div class="mx-auto mb-10 max-w-7xl px-6 md:mb-20 xl:px-0">
  <div class="relative flex flex-col items-center border-2 border-white/20 rounded-lg backdrop-blur-sm bg-white/5">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
      <svg class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 h-full w-full fill-white/20" aria-hidden="true">
        <defs>
          <pattern id="dots-about" width="5" height="5" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <circle cx="1" cy="0.5" r="0.5" />
          </pattern>
        </defs>
        <rect width="100%" height="100%" strokeWidth={0} fill="url(#dots-about)" />
      </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="absolute -left-1.5 -top-1.5 h-3 w-3 bg-white/80" />
    <div class="absolute -bottom-1.5 -left-1.5 h-3 w-3 bg-white/80" />
    <div class="absolute -right-1.5 -top-1.5 h-3 w-3 bg-white/80" />
    <div class="absolute -bottom-1.5 -right-1.5 h-3 w-3 bg-white/80" />

    <div class="relative z-20 mx-auto max-w-5xl rounded-[40px] py-6 md:p-10 xl:py-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white [text-shadow:_0_4px_20px_rgb(0_0_0_/_60%)] mb-6 md:mb-8 font-open-sans-custom">
        About This Template
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 md:space-y-6">
        <p class="text-base md:text-xl lg:text-2xl xl:text-3xl text-white/90 [text-shadow:_0_2px_10px_rgb(0_0_0_/_50%)] font-open-sans-custom leading-relaxed">
          We believe building beautiful, functional products should be simple. This template shows how AI and smart
          prompting make it easy to turn ideas into clean, professional interfaces.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base md:text-xl lg:text-2xl xl:text-3xl text-white/90 [text-shadow:_0_2px_10px_rgb(0_0_0_/_50%)] font-open-sans-custom leading-relaxed">
          It&apos;s designed to highlight key features, scale with your content, and let your AI-powered product
          shine—without extra setup or complexity.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
